verses.verse: <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>Lord<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%>, O you <S%H5650>servants<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%>, <S%H1984>praise<s%> the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%>.
<S%H1288>Blessed<s%> be the <S%H8034>name<s%> of the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> from this time <S%H6258>forth<s%> and <S%H5704>for<s%> <S%H5769>evermore<s%>.
From the <S%H4217>rising<s%> of the <S%H8121>sun<s%> unto the going <S%H3996>down<s%> of the same the <S%H3068>Lord<s%>'s <S%H8034>name<s%> is to be <S%H1984>praised<s%>.
The <S%H3068>Lord<s%> is <S%H7311>high<s%> above all <S%H1471>nations<s%>, and his <S%H3519>glory<s%> above the <S%H8064>heavens<s%>.
Who is like unto the <S%H3068>Lord<s%> our <S%H430>God<s%>, who <S%H3427>dwells<s%> on <S%H1361>high<s%>,
Who <S%H8213>humbles<s%> himself to <S%H7200>behold<s%> the things that are in <S%H8064>heaven<s%>, and in the <S%H776>earth<s%>!
He raises <S%H6965>up<s%> the <S%H1800>poor<s%> out of the <S%H6083>dust<s%>, and <S%H7311>lifts<s%> the <S%H34>needy<s%> out of the <S%H830>dunghill<s%>;
That he may <S%H3427>set<s%> him with <S%H5081>princes<s%>, even with the <S%H5081>princes<s%> of his <S%H5971>people<s%>.

He makes the childless <S%H6135>woman<s%> to <S%H3427>keep<s%> <S%H1004>house<s%>, and to be a <S%H8056>joyful<s%> <S%H517>mother<s%> of <S%H1121>sons<s%>. <S%H1984>Praise<s%> you the <S%H3050>Lord<s%>.
